      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: 8/15/56",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, LOS ANGELES (100-24442)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCER",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "The following is being furnished to the Bureau for its information in the event an inquiry should be received from the Air Force:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "On 8/14/56, Lt. [REDACTED] and Sgt. [REDACTED],",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "4602nd Air Intelligence Service Squadron, Norton AFB, San",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Bernardino, California, called at this office, accompanied by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] of the Air Information Service.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Lt. [REDACTED] stated he had received a teletype from",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "his headquarters, reflecting that [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Street, Van Nuys, California, had reported that on 7/16/56, a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "spherical vehicle had landed in his back yard, splitting a large",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "tree in two. On 7/30/56, this vehicle returned and on this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "occasion some little green men emerged from the vehicle and invited",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "[REDACTED] to ride in their ship. He supposedly went up with them",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "for approximately 20 minutes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Lt. [REDACTED] stated he had no additional information",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "except that [REDACTED] was believed to be employed in some minor",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "technical capacity for the Columbia Broadcasting System.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] stated he recalled that the incident",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "reported by [REDACTED] was presented on a CBS television newscast",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "about the time it occurred, and that during the telecast, the split",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "tree was shown, and an interview was had with [REDACTED]. According",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "to Captin [REDACTED], the tenor of the comments by the television announcer",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "was that he placed little credence in the story, but was presenting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "it for what it was worth.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Lt. [REDACTED] stated that he believes the incident reported",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "by [REDACTED] to be utterly ridiculous, but, in accordance with",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "instructions from his headquarters, he must make some inquiry concerning",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "in such a manner as not to result in any publicity indicating",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "an Air Force interest. He inquired if the FBI would conduct investigation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
